Nidorina (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0029: Nidoran♀
Pokémon
#0031: Nidoqueen →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Nidorina (TCG Pocket).

Nidorina has been featured on 14 different cards since it debuted in the Jungle expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Nidorina cards are normally Darkness-type Stage 1 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Nidorina

Nidorina
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
